                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "All sniper rifles have a 2 second combo duration, with the exception of the Lanka , which has a 6 second combo duration. Harkonar Scope at max rank extends this to 14 seconds, and to 18 seconds for Lanka."
                }
              },
              {
