                  "pageId": 980099,
                  "revisionId": 2647362,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The extended combo duration only applies to a stack if the player is already scoped when the previous stack expires. As such, the most efficient combo conservation can either be achieved by always being scoped in, or only every 14 (18) seconds, when the counter decrements."
